          <li>Tickets to sports or entertainment events</li>
          <li>Vacation rentals</li>
          <li>Art work</li>
          <li>Luxury items</li>
          <li>Hand crafted items</li>
          <li>Skills and services</li>
          <li>Re-gift a new, unwanted item</li>
          <li>Coveted or unique dog and cat supplies</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
